{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/react-loadable组件/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Orainsink's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"02c09f74-7adb-5db9-b7c3-682592e0d01d","excerpt":"异步组件 首屏渲染速度一直是SPA页面性能优化的重点. 异步组件是相对于同步组件而言的, 将用户必要操作所使用的组件设为同步组件, 将体积较大但是使用频率较小的组件设为异步组件, 当调用时再借由和 webpack 拉取相应js代码, 这样可以有效降低页面加载时间. React中使用异步组件 react 版本1…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-blog/react-loadable%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/#%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\">异步组件</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-blog/react-loadable%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/#react%E4%B8%AD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\">React中使用异步组件</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-blog/react-loadable%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/#loadablecomponent\"><code class=\"language-text\">@loadable/component</code></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gatsby-blog/react-loadable%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6/#reactlazy\">React.lazy</a></li>\n</ul>","html":"<h1 id=\"异步组件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"异步组件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>异步组件</h1>\n<p>首屏渲染速度一直是SPA页面性能优化的重点.</p>\n<p>异步组件是相对于同步组件而言的, 将用户必要操作所使用的组件设为同步组件, 将体积较大但是使用频率较小的组件设为异步组件, 当调用时再借由<code class=\"language-text\">import</code>和 webpack 拉取相应js代码, 这样可以有效降低页面加载时间.</p>\n<!--more-->\n<h1 id=\"react中使用异步组件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#react%E4%B8%AD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"react中使用异步组件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React中使用异步组件</h1>\n<p>react 版本16+ 之后<code class=\"language-text\">react-loadable</code>因为停止维护, 不支持webpack4+及Babel v7, 现已不建议使用.</p>\n<p>可选方案为react 16.6 新增方法<code class=\"language-text\">React.lazy</code>及流行的库<code class=\"language-text\">@loadable/component</code></p>\n<p>两者区别参考<a href=\"https://loadable-components.com/docs/loadable-vs-react-lazy/\">Comparison with React.lazy</a></p>\n<p>两者最大的区别是<code class=\"language-text\">React.lazy</code>不能进行服务器端渲染. </p>\n<h1 id=\"loadablecomponent\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#loadablecomponent\" aria-label=\"loadablecomponent permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><code class=\"language-text\">@loadable/component</code></h1>\n<p>简洁明了,看文档就行, <a href=\"https://loadable-components.com/docs/getting-started/\">文档</a> </p>\n<h1 id=\"reactlazy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reactlazy\" aria-label=\"reactlazy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>React.lazy</h1>\n<p>react官方文档: <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/code-splitting.html#reactlazy\">文档</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"react-异步组件lazy or @loadable component","date":"2020/03/09","description":null,"tags":["前端","react"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/react-loadable组件/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/当react遇上gsap3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"当react遇上gsap3"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/性能优化-减少重排重绘/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"性能优化-减少重排重绘"}}}}}